issue.title: [CF 183] Editing Metaicons blocked
issue.body:
Starting with version r56 a dialogue called TellMeWhen_IconEditorMain has begun obscuring significant portions of the meta icon editor. The buttons to add, delete or rearrange the first 5 subicons aren't clickable as a result.


> Posted by CurseForge user AmeroGer | Imported from CurseForge issue #183 | Raw
